Web: http://sourceforge.net/p/usb-vhci/wiki/Home/
     http://sourceforge.net/projects/usb-vhci/

You also need the kernel module for this to work. Download it from:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/usb-vhci/files/linux%20kernel%20module/

Install
=======

Just run

  ./configure
  make
  make install   # (as root)

to build and install it.

If the documentation won't build, try "./configure --disable-doc".
